column2: No zebra mussels were found on the monitoring plates. In addition- there were no zebrta mussels observed on docks or boat lifts that were taken out.
Zebra Mussel monitoring plates in from 5/26/2014 to 10/19/2014.  Found 7 Zebra Mussels on monitoring plates.  First year on monitoring plates.  Did not find any when taking out dock or boat lifts.
No zebra mussels found on monitoring plates- or on dock and boat lifts when removed from water.
